        "content": "<p>/poll What should be the <code>simp</code> normal forms for <code>Iio ⊤</code> and <code>Ico a ⊤</code>?<br>\n<code>Iio ⊤</code> and <code>Ico a ⊤</code><br>\n<code>{⊤}ᶜ</code> and <code>Ico a ⊤</code><br>\n<code>Iio ⊤</code> and <code>Ici a \\ {⊤}</code><br>\n<code>{⊤}ᶜ</code> and <code>Ici a \\ {⊤}</code></p>",
        "id": 283230762,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1653224015
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Note that we simplify <code>Ici ⊤</code> to <code>{⊤}</code>.</p>",
